---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Daxxify | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Daxxify is a next-gen botulinum toxin A designed for longer duration. FDA-approved for glabellar lines. Onset in ~1–2 days and results that can last around 6 months in many patients.',
  canonical: '/services/daxxify/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'Daxxify for Glabellar Lines',
      serviceType: 'Neurotoxin treatment',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      },
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/daxxify/'
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Injectables</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Daxxify</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        A next-generation neuromodulator engineered with a proprietary peptide stabilizer for a longer-lasting
        softening of frown lines—designed to maintain natural expression with thoughtful dosing.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Onset</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">~1–2 days</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Peak</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">2–4 weeks</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Typical Duration</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">~6 months</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Minimal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">

      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Daxxify (daxibotulinumtoxinA-lanm) is a modern botulinum toxin type A approved to temporarily improve
            moderate to severe glabellar lines (the “11s”). Its peptide-stabilized formulation is designed to enhance
            binding efficiency and extend duration, while our conservative approach keeps your expression looking natural.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
            <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              FDA indication: glabellar frown lines
            </li>
            <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              Peptide-stabilized design for longer-lasting effect
            </li>
            <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              Onset typically in 1–2 days; result can last around 6 months
            </li>
            <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              Conservative, anatomy-guided dosing for subtle, balanced outcomes
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Benefits at a glance</h3>
            <div class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-4">
                <div class="font-medium">Longer maintenance window</div>
                <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">Many patients enjoy visible improvement for about 6 months.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-4">
                <div class="font-medium">Subtle, natural finish</div>
                <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">Relaxation without looking “overdone.”</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-4">
                <div class="font-medium">Efficient onset</div>
                <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">Early softening can be noticed within 1–2 days.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-4">
                <div class="font-medium">Thoughtful protocols</div>
                <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">Clear aftercare and optional follow-up for fine-tuning.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            A streamlined in-office visit focused on precision and comfort. Most clients return to normal routines right away.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Before your visit</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Share medical history, medications, and prior treatments.</li>
                <li>Arrive with clean skin on the treatment area.</li>
                <li>We’ll outline goals, dosing, and expected timeline.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">During treatment</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Precise micro-injections with a fine needle.</li>
                <li>Glabellar area typically uses five points.</li>
                <li>Session time is usually just a few minutes.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 sm:col-span-2">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Timeline</div>
              <div class="mt-2 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm text-neutral-700">
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-3">
                  <div class="font-medium">Day 1–2</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-neutral-600">Early softening for many patients.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-3">
                  <div class="font-medium">Weeks 2–4</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-neutral-600">Result stabilizes; review if needed.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-3">
                  <div class="font-medium">Up to ~6 mo.</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-neutral-600">Gradual return of movement over time.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Stay upright for several hours and avoid rubbing or massaging treated areas for 24 hours.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Skip strenuous workouts and heavy heat exposure (saunas, very hot showers) for 24–48 hours.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Use cool compresses if needed for swelling, without strong pressure.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid heavy makeup on the area the first day.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Mild redness, tenderness, or small bumps can occur and usually resolve quickly. Contact the clinic
              promptly for notable drooping, difficulty swallowing or breathing, or any unexpected symptoms.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & considerations</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, temporary effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Injection-site tenderness, redness, small bruises</li>
              <li>Headache</li>
              <li>Transient eyelid heaviness or eyebrow asymmetry (uncommon)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Important precautions</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Not advised during pregnancy or breastfeeding</li>
              <li>Avoid if active infection at the site</li>
              <li>Tell your provider about neuromuscular conditions or medicines that affect neuromuscular transmission</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How quickly will I see results and how long do they last?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Early softening is often noticed within 1–2 days, with results stabilizing by weeks 2–4.
              Many patients maintain improvement for about 6 months before movement gradually returns.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Will I look frozen?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Our goal is a relaxed, natural expression—not a fixed look. We dose conservatively and tailor to your anatomy.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Is it only for the frown lines?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              The cosmetic FDA approval is for the glabellar area. Your provider can advise on suitability and timing
              of any additional treatments based on your goals.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Subtle help card -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Curious if Daxxify is right for you? Share your goals and we’ll outline a conservative, natural plan.
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
